00:32:40.833 --> 00:32:45.205
MATT: But being a dragon can be a dragon.

00:32:45.205 --> 00:32:47.758
MARY: Not anymore, Rimefang.

00:32:47.758 --> 00:32:48.915
MATT: Aww...

